               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 5ra-111vb)
 -
                     Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 5ra-10ra) 
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 15vb-22rb)
 - Homily
                     by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     74ra-78va)
 - Prayer of archbishop ʾabbā Sawiros (fols. 90ra-92va)
 -
                     Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.102ra-104vb)
 -
                     Blessing of ʾabuna Sāmuʾel (fols. 109ra-111vb), incomplete</summary>
